                     n="41"/>bhūmi-cchidra-nyāyenā-candrārkka-kṣiti-sama-kālaṁ<g type="danda">.</g> mātā-pitror ātmanaś ca puṇya-yaśo ’bhivr̥ddhaye<g type="danda">.</g> bhagavantaṁ vuddha-bha<lb 
                     n="42" break="no"/>ṭ<supplied reason="omitted">ṭ</supplied>ārakam uddiśya<g type="danda">.</g> bharadvāja-sagotrāya bharadvājāṅgirasa-vārhaspatya-pravarāya maitrāyaṇī-śākhādhyāyine<lb 
                     n="43"/>mīmānsā-vyākaraṇa-tarkka-vidyā-vide tharkkārikā-vinirggata-vidyāpottaka-samvaddha-kaccābhiṣṭikā-<unclear>vāsta</unclear>vyā<lb 
