                 </p>
                 <p n="48">samvat· <num value="5">5</num> phālguna-dine <num value="12">12</num><g type="ddanda">.</g></p>
                 <p n="48">bhavanti cātra dharmmānuśaṁsinaḥ<surplus><g type="danda">.</g></surplus> ślokāḥ<g type="ddanda">.</g></p>
                 <lg n="13" met="anuṣṭubh">
